long_desc.thetext:
I have the same problem. Installing the following module package works for me:

module xxx-virt 1.0;

require {
        type systemd_machined_t;
        type init_t;
        class system start;
}

#============= systemd_machined_t ==============
allow systemd_machined_t init_t:system start;

Thanks, work it!

